Usage: addPinToPinGroup [-help] [-cell <cellName>] -pin {pinName | pinNameList}
                        -pinGroup <pinGroupName>

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>                  # Specifies the name of the module
                                  # (string, optional)
-pin {pinName | pinNameList}      # Specifies the name of module port.
                                  # (string, required)
-pinGroup <pinGroupName>          # Specifies the name of the pin Group of the
                                  # module. (string, required)